"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-21-ready-say-paris-olympics-organisers\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - Paris Olympics supremo Tony Estanguet said Sunday that the city was \\\"ready\\\" for the Games as he played down complaints from some residents and businesses about the impact of the event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris Olympics supremo\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 44}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 77, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 111}, {\"ngram\": \"complaints\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"some residents\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"businesses\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 175}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 192}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are ready as we head into the final phase,\\\" Estanguet told a press conference in Paris, five days from the opening parade next Friday.\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 293, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.071307068645821e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final phase\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening parade\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"For as long as the closing ceremony has not finished, we need to remain vigilant.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But today we are exactly where we would have dreamed of being a few years ago.\\\"\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Finishing touches are being applied to the venues across the City of Light and thousands of athletes and officials are pouring in, while the weather has also brightened up after months of rain.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Finishing touches\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"rain\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a further boost for organisers, the water quality of the river Seine - which is set to be used for outdoor Olympic swimming events - has also improved dramatically since the start of July.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.5990647753031143e-13, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a further boost\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"the water quality\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"outdoor Olympic swimming events\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the indicators for the Seine are positive at this stage,\\\" Estanguet added.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.5990647753031143e-13, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the indicators\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The river is set to host the opening ceremony next Friday which will see 6,000-7,000 athletes sail down it on 85 barges and boats.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The river\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"6,000-7,000 athletes\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"85 barges\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be the first time a Summer Olympics has opened outside the main athletics stadium, with up to 300,000 ticketed spectators set to watch from stands and on the river banks and another 200,000 expected to watch from the overlooking apartments.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"a Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"the main athletics stadium\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 300,000 ticketed spectators\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"stands\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"the river banks\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"the overlooking apartments\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 4,000 tickets are still available, Estanguet said.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around 4,000 tickets\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have always tried to maintain as high a level of ambition as possible so that these Games make France shine,\\\" Estanguet added.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9914359963859201, \"rank\": 0.006202169282270568, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as high a level\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"ambition\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vast security operation required for the opening ceremony is causing some friction, however, with large parts of central Paris along the banks of the river and around Olympic venues off-limits for most people.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1689, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.071307068645821e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vast security operation\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"some friction\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"large parts\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\